Package: STA380Project
Title: Simulating Kumaraswamy and Arcsine Distributions
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Christian Jason", "Sumitro", , "christian.sumitro@mail.utoronto.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    person("Handaru", "Ashshidiqie", , "handaru.ashshidiqie@mail.utoronto.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    person("Khoi", "Ho", , "khoi.ho@mail.utoronto.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package uses pure simulation to generate random variables from the Kumaraswamy and Arcsine distributions. It utilizes the Inverse Transform Sampling method applied to the Uniform distribution to verify that simulated samples match their theoretical density curves.
